   112|# ============================================
   113|# Country Targeting (Optional)
   114|# ============================================
   115|# TARGET_COUNTRIES is a Python list of ISO-3166 country codes used for
   116|# country-rotation scanning in Shodan, FOFA, and URLScan.
   117|# Defaults to a built-in list of 50 high-Telegram-usage countries.
   118|# Override by setting a JSON array: TARGET_COUNTRIES=["US","DE","RU"]
   119|# Leave unset to use the default list.
   120|# TARGET_COUNTRIES=
